items.name: CUSTOM_WITH_NO_FCOE_VC_INACTIVE_OV_INACTIVE
Quality of Service

issues.description: Profile "Profile_3" Ethernet connection 2 does not have an associated network. This connection will not be migrated because OneView does not allow server profile connections without an assigned network.
issues.recommendation: To migrate the server profile connection, assign a network to this connection. If virtual MAC addresses are configured, assigning a network to this connection will preserve these addresses.

issues.description: Profile "Profile_3" FCoE connection 1 is configured for factory MAC and a factory WWN of 10:00:6C:C2:17:2C:43:A1. The WWN for this connection may change after migration to OneView.
issues.recommendation: After the migration task has completed, validate the WWNs of the migrated profiles for any potential changes. If a WWN change occurred, change the SAN fabric and storage configuration to reflect the new WWNs before powering on the servers.
